title: 3 Ways to Know How Long it Takes to Fall in Love
description: How long should it take to fall in love?Is what you’re experiencing the real thing or is it just infatuation?Whether you have just started dating someone and felt love immediately or if you’ve been in a relationship for a long time and still aren’t sure where it’s going, here are 3 ways to find out how long it might take for you to truly fall in love with someone.
author: onpurposepodcast@jayshetty.me (Jay Shetty)
